    <updated>2022-05-04T10:34:41.903Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>目录</strong></p><ul><li><a href="#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82:">功能需求:</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8:">设备列表:</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B:">实现过程:</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95:">访问方法:</a></li></ul><p>[(ง •_•)ง 谢谢阅读!](#(ง •_•)ง 谢谢阅读!)</p><hr><h2 id="功能需求"><a href="#功能需求" class="headerlink" title="功能需求:"></a>功能需求:</h2><ol><li>电脑或手机端,能够随时连接到,外接在机顶盒上的移动硬盘或U盘.</li><li>机顶盒能够正常看电视,并且开机自动启用FTP功能.</li></ol><h2 id="设备列表"><a href="#设备列表" class="headerlink" title="设备列表:"></a>设备列表:</h2><ul><li>机顶盒 (安装有当贝市场,至于怎么安装刷机包,我也是百度的)</li><li>显示器</li><li>硬盘,U盘</li><li>电脑</li></ul><hr><h2 id="实现过程"><a href="#实现过程" class="headerlink" title="实现过程:"></a>实现过程:</h2><p>我使用的机顶盒是 创维E900S 芯片为S905L,其他机顶盒可以在当贝社区里面找ROM包</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2774deea702f4e44bf99222aff9dbffb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2774deea702f4e44bf99222aff9dbffb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/18d63e1a8fad408e80608fe2db4ba600.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/18d63e1a8fad408e80608fe2db4ba600.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><h3 id="刷机包以及方法"><a href="#刷机包以及方法" class="headerlink" title="刷机包以及方法:"></a>刷机包以及方法:</h3><p><a href="https://www.znds.com/rom/741079.html">创维E900-ST高安版-S905L芯片ROM固件<img src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" alt=" " srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" class="lozad post-image">https://www.znds.com/rom/741079.html</a></p><p><a href="https://www.znds.com/rom/down/">当贝社区链接<img src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" alt=" " srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" class="lozad post-image">https://www.znds.com/rom/down/</a></p><p><a href="http://www.meibu.com/soft/ftp.apk">“每步FTP”软件下载地址<img src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" alt=" " srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release2.0.7/ckeditor/plugins/CsdnLink/icons/icon-default.png?t=M1L8" class="lozad post-image">http://www.meibu.com/soft/ftp.apk</a></p><p>1.机顶盒刷机成功以后,打开当贝桌面,安装”小白文件管理器app” 使用里面的文件传输功能,上传”每步FTP”app,并安装. 也可以使用当贝自带的上传工具.</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/39414a4e49064a0ebf031d8f83e3fccf.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/39414a4e49064a0ebf031d8f83e3fccf.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p>2.外接一个U盘或硬盘</p><p>3.打开”小白资源管理器”–文件管理–查看U盘,硬盘路径.</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/180bacc6c97646cbb6bc800fd18518da.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/180bacc6c97646cbb6bc800fd18518da.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p>4.打开”每步FTP”–设置–更改路径为硬盘路径.</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/03d4352673904ddaaaa5ac7a86291eca.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/03d4352673904ddaaaa5ac7a86291eca.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p>5.开启”匿名登录”,”保持设备唤醒”–返回</p><p>6.开启FTP服务,成功以后会显示ftp地址</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b8da76a7e9964af79baa9f4b0a836949.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b8da76a7e9964af79baa9f4b0a836949.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/56c6c77c1db14cddb422ad7c26eeed02.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/56c6c77c1db14cddb422ad7c26eeed02.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p>**建议:**路由器端分配一个静态ip给机顶盒,不然ftp地址会变.</p><p>**注释:**其实”小白文件管理器”自带FTP功能,但是不能开启自动启用FTP服务,且不能更改FTP映 射路径,所以使用”每步FTP”,网上找了好久才找到这个软件.</p><h2 id="访问方法"><a href="#访问方法" class="headerlink" title="访问方法:"></a>访问方法:</h2><h3 id="电脑端-gt"><a href="#电脑端-gt" class="headerlink" title="电脑端&gt;"></a>电脑端&gt;</h3><p>​    方法一:直接在资源管理器中输入FTP地址,例如”<a href="ftp://192.168.10.10:2121/">ftp://192.168.10.10:2121/</a>“–回车即可访问.</p><p>​    <img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fd129a8861c544148f1c7433be90a051.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_13,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fd129a8861c544148f1c7433be90a051.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_13,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><p>​    方法二:新建一个网络位置,按向导提示,输入FTP地址,下次可以直接在资源管理器中点击访问.</p><p>​    <img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c16708be66d64776ae43d661142e46fa.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_17,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c16708be66d64776ae43d661142e46fa.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAVUtlcnNMaW5r,size_17,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" class="lozad post-image"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="点击并拖拽以移动" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" class="lozad post-image"></p><h3 id="手机端-gt"><a href="#手机端-gt" class="headerlink" title="手机端&gt;"></a>手机端&gt;</h3><p>​    下载es文件管理器等软件,里面有FTP服务,连接统一局域网,输入地址即可访问.</p><h1 id="ง-•-•-ง-谢谢阅读"><a href="#ง-•-•-ง-谢谢阅读" class="headerlink" title="(ง •_•)ง 谢谢阅读!"></a>(ง •_•)ง 谢谢阅读!</h1>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
